179906.name: Share of global cumulative CO2 emissions from other industry
179906.description: Cumulative production-based emissions of carbon dioxide (CO2) from other industry sources since the first year of data availability, measured as a percentage of global cumulative production-based emissions of CO2 from other industry sources since the first year of data availability. This is based on territorial emissions, which do not account for emissions embedded in traded goods. Each country's share of global CO2 emissions from other industry sources has been calculated by Our World in Data using global CO2 emissions from other industry sources provided in the Global Carbon Budget dataset. Global emissions from other industry sources include all country emissions.
